\id PHM - Bible Kiyaka 
\h FIDIMONI 
\toc3 Fdm 
\toc2 Fidimoni 
\toc1 Mukanda kwena Fidimoni 
\mt2 Mukanda kwena Fidimoni 
\mt1 Fidimoni 
\imt1 Khotidi ya mukanda 
\ip Fidimoni kenina nduku wa thumwa Pholu. Pholu kámusamwana Musamu wa Bukheti ku nima, wákituka mukidisitu. Mukyedika kenina mvwama. Kákala yi bahika. Onezimi, mosi wa bahika ba Fidimoni, wátina kwena pfumu wandi. Kámuwana Pholu muna boloku mwamuna kákala. Wákituka mukidisitu yandi phi. Pholu wámuvutula Onezimi kwena pfumu wandi yi mukanda hana moku. Abweti Fidimoni kamúyambila Onezimi? 
\ip Mukanda wa Pholu kwena Fidimoni wutadidini phi kimvuka kina kyisi khundakanina muna nzu yandi (nzila 2). Wubati zonzila dyambu dimosi ditadidini kimvuka kya muthu. 
\ip Muna tangwa meni dyadina, kimvwama kya bisi Loma kyákala mu kikhita kya bahika. Ndambu mosi ya batu ba mulambu wawuna benina bahika. Babati sala muna bisalu byosu amana luzingu lwa bawu lwosu ha moku ma bapfumu ba bawu. Kutina kwa muhika bisikwa hanina ndola mosi ya ngolu, mbala za hika mu lufwa. 
\ip Muna mukanda wandi, Pholu kabati lomba kwena Fidimoni mu kumutambula Onezimi hanga phangi watondama. Kikuma boosu, yi batu bana bakondi kala bahika yi bahika, benina baphangi mwena Kidisitu. Kaasi Pholu kabatiku hana muswa kwena Fidimoni. Wuzodini ni Fidimoni kabonga lukanu yandi meni mu mana kasála. 
\ip Bakidisitu ba theti báfwanaku kedi mu kubalumuna mutindu wa luzingu lwa bawu muna mbala mosi. Kaasi lukwikilu mwena Yesu Kidisitu lubalumuni mutindu wa kuzingila muna mbala mosi. Ndinga ya lungongu yenina yi ndandu muna luzingu lwa kingenga yi luzingu lwa batu boosu. 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Yandu meni Pholu, bákotisa mu boloku kikuma kya Kidisitu Yesu yi phangi Thimoti. 
\p Kwena ngeyi Fidimoni, watondama yi musindikidi wetu wa kisalu,  
\v 2 yi kwena Aphiya, phangi wetu wa mukhetu, kwena Adisiphi, musindikidi wetu wa mizingu, yi kwena Dibundu dina dyisi khundakana muna nzu yaku:  
\v 3 Yambula Nzambi Tata wetu yi Pfumu wetu Yesu Kidisitu baluheka khenda yi ngemba. 
\s1 Lungongu yi lukwikilu lwa Fidimoni 
\p  
\v 4 Mbala zoosu zina yisi vutula matondu kwena Nzambi wama, yisi tumbula zina dyaku Fidimoni muna bisambu byama.  
\v 5 Mukuma yisi yuka khululuka ya lungongu lwaku kikuma kya bakwikidi boosu yi lukwikilu lwaku kwena Pfumu Yesu.  
\v 6 Yisi lomba kwena Nzambi ni lukwikilu luna wenina lwawu mu kithwadi yi betu, lwakala ngolu mwena ngeyi ndangu lwasongila mamboti mana tufwani mu kulungisa kikuma kya Kidisitu.  
\v 7 Kikuma, zola dyaku, phangi, dipheki kyesi kya lawu yi kikesa, mukuma wusyamisini mbundu ya bakwikidi. 
\s1 Pholu wulombi lusadisu kikuma kya Onezimi 
\p  
\v 8 Yihana ni, mbatanana yenina yi muswa mu kithwadi yi Kidisitu mu kukusenda mana wulungini mu kuhanga,  
\v 9 kaasi nzodi yikulomba kima kimosi muna zina dya lungongu. Bwosu yekina, meni Pholu, kinunu, amana phi buthwena mu boloku yenina kikuma kya Kidisitu Yesu,  
\v 10 mbati kulomba lusadisu kikuma kya Mwana wama Onezimi. Yandi Kenina mwana wama wuna mbutidini muna boloku.  
\v 11 Theti, kákalaku mupfunu kwena ngeyi, kaasi buthwena bwabu, mupfunu katuyekina kwena ngeyi yi meni. 
\p  
\v 12 Buthwena, yikuvutwadi yandi, yandi wenina hanga ndambu ya meni meni.  
\v 13 Yizodi ni kakala bela-bela yi meni ndangu katsadisaka ha kifulu kya ngeyi, muna tangwa dyadi yenina mu boloku kikuma kya Musamu wa Bukheti.  
\v 14 Kaasi nzodikiku ni yihanga kima konda wapheka nzila, ndangu wuhangaku mambu mu kingolu-ngolu kaasi yi mbundu ya bukheti. 
\p  
\v 15 Ngatu Onezimi káyekukila kwena ngeyi kikuma kya tangwa dya khunda, ndangu kakuvutwakila kyamakulu,  
\v 16 kakalaku hanga muhika wa ngeyi, kaasi wekina kuhita muhika: phangi mosi watondama. Mukuma kenina kwena meni, hanga phangi watondama, kakálabwa hika kwena ngeyi phi phangi watondama, hanga mutu, hanga phi phangi mwena Kidisitu. 
\p  
\v 17 Yuka ni wisi mbongila hanga nduku waku, mubonga yandi phi bwosu wisi mbongila meni.  
\v 18 Yuka ni mbi kákuhanga, kondi loni pfuka yaku kenina yawu, syabya mu mutwa wa meni.  
\v 19 Yi koku dya meni meni mbati sonikina mambu mama: Meni Pholu, yikúvutwalabya. Nzodiku yikuyubululabwa ni ngeyi pfuka ya meni wenina yawu, luzingu lwaku yáta.  
\v 20 Kyedika, Phangi wama, tsadisa bwabuna kikuma kya lungongu lwa Pfumu: ndembika mbundu mukuma ngeyi yi meni kima kimosi thwenina mwena Kidisitu. 
\p  
\v 21 Tsini mbundu ni muna tangwa dyadidi mbati kusonikina, wahánga kuhita hika buna yikulombini. Nzayi mboti ni wahángabwa hika kuluta.  
\v 22 Amana muna mbala mosi, yikulombi hika ni wangidikila mwanza, mukuma yenina yi kikwamina ni muna bisambu byenu nzila yakhángwakila ndangu yisa luvutwakila hika. 
\s1 Mboti za tsuka 
\p  
\v 23 Ephafwasi, yandi wenina hakimosi yi meni mu boloku kikuma kya Kidisitu Yesu, mboti kakuhekini;  
\v 24 Malaku, Adisitadiki, Temasi yi Luka, basindikidi bama ba kisalu, bawu phi mboti bakuhekini. 
\p  
\v 25 Yambula khenda za Pfumu Yesu Kidisitu zakala yi kitembu kyenu!